elfeckcom
===============================================================================
(*) This is the source for my new website. You might visit it at elfeck.com
(*) I'm not good at haskell and/or scotty so don't expect much


content format
===============================================================================
(*) Meta
    > Creation Time Stamp
    > Modify Time Stamp
    > Access level
    > Type

(*) Content
    > Title
    > Categories
    > Content

(*) Types
    0: Website Main Post
    1: Blog Post
    2: Twitter-like Snippet

(*) Submit Types
    0: Inset
    1: Update
    2: Delete


MD to html parsing
===============================================================================
(*) To Handle
    > Headline		==
    > Linebreaks	double space
    > New paragraph	empty line
    > i	  		* *
    > b			** **
    > link		[name](url)
    > img		![name](url)